Name: Sky Conqueror
About the game: The game tells a story about a crazy skydiver, who decided that for an extreme jump with a parachute... he doesn't need a parachute. Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of air travel, avoid obstacles, dodge them, maneuver... Do everything to make the dream of the extreme - conquer the sky - come true! Key features: Dynamic gameplay Gradually increasing complexity Online leaderboard Achievements system Minimalistic graphics
